            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": "Understanding your repair and pipe material options helps you make informed decisions about water leak repairs. Not all leaks require the same repair approach, and material selection significantly impacts long-term reliability and cost-effectiveness. This decision guide explains when each repair method is appropriate and which pipe materials work best for Tucson's challenging water conditions."
