            "content": "Upon arrival, our licensed master plumber will introduce themselves, present credentials, and discuss your specific leak concerns and symptoms you've observed. We'll conduct a detailed visual inspection of all plumbing fixtures, accessible pipes, water heater, and areas where you've noticed problems. Using your water meter, we'll perform a baseline leak test—shutting off all water usage and monitoring the meter for movement indicating active leaks. If movement is detected, we know a leak exists somewhere in your system."
